---
// No icons needed for this component
---

<section class="py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] relative">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      
      <!-- Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 shrink-0">
        <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] md:aspect-square bg-gray-800 overflow-hidden border border-gray-700 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
           <!-- Using a tech-focused professional placeholder -->
           <img 
             src="https://picsum.photos/400/500?grayscale" 
             alt="Engenheiro de Negócios" 
             class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80"
           />
           <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent">
             <p class="font-mono text-yellow-500 text-xs uppercase">Founder & Lead Engineer</p>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-industrial text-white mb-8 uppercase leading-tight">
          49 Anos. Background de <span class="text-yellow-500">Engenharia</span> e Negócios.
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Não sou um gestor de tráfego tentando vender automação. Sou um especialista em infraestrutura de negócios.
          </p>
          <p>
            Minha carreira atravessou do Flash à IA Generativa. Eu não brinco de prompt. Eu construo sistemas que substituem departamentos inteiros.
          </p>
          <p class="border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-6 text-white font-medium">
            "Quando eu entro na reunião com seu cliente, eu sou o 'Adulto na Sala' que garante que a tecnologia vai funcionar."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
          <div class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded text-xs font-mono text-gray-400">n8n Expert</div>
          <div class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded text-xs font-mono text-gray-400">Python Infrastructure</div>
          <div class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-900 border border-gray-700 rounded text-xs font-mono text-gray-400">Business Logic</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

